  (text "ESP32-C3-MINI-1 Module Notes:\n\nDecoupling: C30/C31 = 100nF + 10uF near VDD\nAntenna keep-out: 15mm clear area above module\nGPIO0/1: UART0 to STM32 (cross-connected TX↔RX)\nGPIO2/3: I2C to SSD1306 OLED (4.7k pullups)\nGPIO8: WS2812 data (series 470R resistor)\nGPIO7: User button (internal pullup)\nUSB D-/D+: GPIO18/GPIO19 with USBLC6-2 ESD"
